channel.title: 100% god wars npcs! [508++++++++++]~~~~~~~~~
channel.description:
I made a unique God Wars spawn. WHY? Because it has 100% of the NPC spawns. It's not the best bot semi-realistic. I did no bot and take the coords like some other people did. There are sometimes too much or too little of NPC's I will try to even it out but it is MUCH more better than any 508 right now. I highly recommend using this. I put this in Tutorials because I get more views. No noobs read Configuration and I would really like to see this in servers (even if they are leeched)
I have: Jogres Orks Goblins Imps Pyrefiends Saradomin Warriors Spiritual Rangers (Saradomin) Spiritual Mages (Zamorak) Avansies (Varies) Spiritual Mages (Armadyl)
AND MUCH more, these NPC's are not included in any server.
There are no walkpaths for the NPCs but the spawns are fully completed. Remeber there is a Saradomin Chamber that has Height as 1. If you want to access height 1 add the object for it.
So, sorry to keep you waiting: [url=http://uppit.com/v/4EROZQQN]http://uppit.com/v/4EROZQQN[/url]
This is the NPC list Emotes, HP (ECT) here: [url=http://www.google.org/showthread.php?t=175219]http://www.google.org/showthread.php?t=175219[/url]
Pics: VVVCLICK HERE TO SEE IF YOU COMPUTER IS GOOD [IMG]http://i34.tinypic.com/r02yqo.png[/img] Note: Since there are no walkpaths, God Wars may look strange.
Enjoy! If you ever add those NPC info please post the God Wars npcs in Npclist.cfg
Credits: Serentiy and Laxixka for providing me with his extremely useful source Me for spawning all the NPCs and releasing it and Palidino76, his God Wars made me feel envious. :)
